  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 11</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 27 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 15 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 31</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob, P</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus and empower your bones, sending them through the ground to rip through the area, dealing 6d12 piercing damage. The area remains littered with giant bone spikes, as if a thick forest of trees, which you can merge and move through (as per Mokuton: Kiugoku no Jutsu, but only allowing movement through the bone spikes). The bones are 10 to 15 feet tall, and count as though they were Large trees. Once dismissed or the duration expires, the bones wither and crumble. This technique can be used while underground and within 5 ft of the surface.</p>\n\n\n\n",
